"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdc6706fdfc740ee6243019a6234a738d67aa44","tid":218520,"uid":31423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:28:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解咁撚多人吹奏梁朝偉個樣<br />\n公平d計全盛時期既話梁朝偉最多未對眼好睇過梁家輝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係要計樣 劉德華先係最撚靚仔</blockquote><br />\n下我覺得朝偉靚仔過華仔<br />\n隻眼好深遂 係無間道入面型過華仔</blockquote><br />\n我覺得華仔係靚仔+英氣，偉仔靚仔+氣質"},{"pid":"6c49c431149187c03a6c5c2b2fe5815cb71a9eed","tid":218520,"uid":70448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T13:42:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲有樓上有講梁家輝唔型，係咪無睇過東邪西毒，佢做黃藥師架喎，仲有情人呢，鬼佬都話佢型架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s25.postimg.org/nfz6bps1b/5d2ae9a421db278bb221532b6050789f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs25.postimg.org%2Fnfz6bps1b%2F5d2ae9a421db278bb221532b6050789f.jpg&h=ab8c2f72&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n根本梁家輝型到震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係花靚can個類囉⋯⋯</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n話梁家輝樣衰班戇鳩睇過佢舊時d戲未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然我都認為偉仔電眼幾殺食<br />\n但梁家輝唔止型，仲好有男人味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細細個已經覺得佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4c1f083af6e17f4e1fba56da1d085fbaf25bab3","tid":218520,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:18:48.000Z","msg":"Honestly，梁家輝has nicer ass"},{"pid":"5cacaeb350b2c2cff212774df9fd9c53311de4f5","tid":218520,"uid":21161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T14:25:18.000Z","msg":"其實梁家輝實力真係好強<br />\n演員最重要係咩？<br />\